 Laurent)\n\nhttps://www.openstreetmap.org/node/2505201225\n\nℙ𝕠𝕤
 𝕥𝕖𝕣 𝕞𝕒𝕜𝕚𝕟𝕘\nDIRA - 2035 Saint-Laurent\, 3rd flo
 or\nMay 23rd - 12 pm\nYou’re invited to a glittery poster making session
 . All the material and a lunch will be provided. S*x workers and allies ar
