LOCATION:(online)
DESCRIPTION:2026-05-26 09:00:00\n\n(online)\n\nWhat is the Permanent Peopl
 es’ Tribunal?\nThe Permanent Peoples’ Tribunal (PPT) is an independent
 \, international opinion tribunal that investigates human rights violation
